formula showing that\nthe difference between the critical energy densities of O$(n)$ models and that\nof the Ising model is smaller than $1\\%$ if $n<8$ and never exceeds $3\\%$ for\nany $n$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Jul 2014 08:22:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-07-29"}
