ius with the new mass\nestimates results in a planetary density of $ 1.19 \\pm 0.27\\, \\rho_{\\oplus}$\nwhich is consistent with a rocky composition. The CoRoT-7 system remains an\nexcellent test bed for the effects of activity in the derivation of planetary\nparameters in the shallow transit regime.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Jul 2014 15:41:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-22"}
